import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['fertility'] = pd.to_numeric(data['fertility'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='fertility', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['fertility'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['fertility'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of fertility across all countries?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['life_expect'] = pd.to_datetime(data['life_expect'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    sns.boxplot(x='country', y='life_expect', data=data)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.title('How does life expectancy vary across different countries?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['fertility'] = pd.to_numeric(data['fertility'], errors='coerce')
    avg_fertility = data.groupby('country')['fertility'].mean().reset_index()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='country', y='fertility', data=avg_fertility)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90)
    plt.title('What is the average fertility rate for each country?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['year', 'n_fertility', 'n_life_expect'])
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='year', y='n_fertility', data=data, label='Normalized Fertility Rate')
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='year', y='n_life_expect', data=data, label='Normalized Life Expectancy')
    plt.title('How does the normalized fertility rate compare to the normalized life expectancy?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
